Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:11.61,main,aki,0,0,0,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.85,main,aki,0,0,0,,Almost got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.49,sign_338_3_Opponent_has_los,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(170,200)\fad(277,1)}Opponent has lost connection.\NPlease remain on this screen until result is determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.21,main,aki,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.14,main,aki,0,0,0,,They always disconnect the \Nminute I start dominating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:22.45,main,aki,0,0,0,,I'll never move up the \Nleaderboard like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.59,main,aki,0,0,0,,It might be time to stop playing this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:27.13,sign_606_8_Konpeito,sign,0,0,0,,Konpeito
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.99,main,aki,0,0,0,,Time for school, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.60,sign_933_10_A_Day_s_Worth_of,sign,0,0,0,,{\fay-.34\pos(138,158)\fscx90}A Day's Worth of Veggies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.28,main,aki,0,0,0,,"Key"—perfect name for a latchkey kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:02.73,main,aki,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:09.17,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I want to play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.46,italics,aki,0,0,0,,A game to get immersed in, for however long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:14.92,italics,aki,0,0,0,,A game to escape this reality of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:17.59,main,a,0,0,0,,Say, isn't that Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:20.38,main,a,0,0,0,,Wow. He's even gaming on the walk to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:23.27,main,a,0,0,0,,He's at it all day {\i1}at{\i0} school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.38,main,a,0,0,0,,He never stops during classes or breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.35,main,b,0,0,0,,But he's always top of the class \Non the standardized tests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:31.34,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Getting good grades is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:33.55,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Formulas, grammar, vocabulary...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:36.94,italics,aki,0,0,0,,They're just testing how \Nmuch you can memorize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.30,main,a,0,0,0,,Point is, he's a total weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.27,main,b,0,0,0,,Hush! He'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.00,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I agree with her, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:49.05,italics,aki,0,0,0,,They say exams are a battlefield, \Nbut they're barely even a competition for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.95,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I can't engage with them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.30,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Receive a variety of objectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.36,italics,aki,0,0,0,,then beat the enemies \Nor clear the obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:59.61,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Games like that are the only \Nthings I can really engage with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:06.11,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's why I find my current \Nreality so very bor—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:12.72,main,driver,0,0,0,,What's your problem, asshole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.81,italics,aki,0,0,0,,He's only after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.71,italics,aki,0,0,0,,What's this guy's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.14,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Should I call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.69,italics,aki,0,0,0,,But I can't do that while I'm fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.07,italics,aki,0,0,0,,He'll catch me before I shake him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.22,italics,aki,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.40,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I need a counter-strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:55.15,italics,aki,0,0,0,,A counter-strategy... almost like a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.37,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.13,italics,aki,0,0,0,,The loss condition is, "He catches me."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.41,italics,aki,0,0,0,,And the win condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.69,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.53,italics,aki,0,0,0,,If I treat it like a game, \NI'll know just what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:10.00,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That building would give \Nme the terrain advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.14,italics,aki,0,0,0,,This building was abandoned \Nin the middle of demolition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.12,italics,aki,0,0,0,,It's been left to the elements, crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.50,italics,aki,0,0,0,,For a big brute like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.09,italics,aki,0,0,0,,It'll take time to make his way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.71,italics,aki,0,0,0,,He just jumped it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.99,italics,aki,0,0,0,,What a freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.06,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I'd better treat this \Nscenario like survival horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.53,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I have to anticipate his next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.17,main,aki,0,0,0,,Hey! Freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.29,main,aki,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.81,main,aki,0,0,0,,He's still not down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.28,main,aki,0,0,0,,He's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.47,main,aki,0,0,0,,With jumping power like his, he'll definitely—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.58,main,aki,0,0,0,,{\i1}attempt{\i0} to jump his way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.00,main,aki,0,0,0,,With sufficient planning and preparation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.73,main,aki,0,0,0,,any game can be beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.32,main,mion,0,0,0,,Congratulations to you, Akira Shiroyanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:57.26,main,mion,0,0,0,,Who'd have believed you'd beat \Nmy little pet and survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.07,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.07,italics,aki,0,0,0,,How long has she—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.73,main,mion,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.19,main,mion,0,0,0,,Even though you worked so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.24,main,mion,0,0,0,,This is what they call...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.17,main,mion,0,0,0,,An unwinnable fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:24.01,main,aki,0,0,0,,I couldn't... anticipate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.30,main,mion,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.25,main,aki,0,0,0,,If it's an unwinnable fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.73,main,aki,0,0,0,,That means... it's not over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.51,main,mion,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.33,main,mion,0,0,0,,The fun's just getting started,\Nmy sweet prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.27,italics,aki,0,0,0,,If the game's not over... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.95,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.51,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I'll win next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.66,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I want to play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.08,italics,aki,0,0,0,,A game to escape this boring reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:29.01,sign_10678_83_Episode_1___Soph,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(415,310)\fad(380,300)}Episode 1   "Sophist"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.84,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.71,main,aki,0,0,0,,Handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.74,main,aki,0,0,0,,Wait, she shot m—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.91,main,aki,0,0,0,,I'm fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:56.12,main,mion,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.81,main,mion,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.36,main,mion,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.80,main,mion,0,0,0,,I'll be serving as your navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.85,main,mion,0,0,0,,The beautiful magician, Mion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:08.81,main,aki,0,0,0,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.17,main,mion,0,0,0,,Let me start with my congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:15.33,main,mion,0,0,0,,You've been chosen to serve as our \Nproject's esteemed focus group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:19.51,main,mion,0,0,0,,I will now explain how it works, with a \Nfew marvelous illusions along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.98,main,mion,0,0,0,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:25.59,main,mion,0,0,0,,Everyone here has already been \Nremoved from the national registry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.71,main,mion,0,0,0,,That's right! You're dead \Nin the eyes of society!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.61,main,yuu,0,0,0,,Dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.87,main,mion,0,0,0,,So it goes without saying that you \Nhave no rights and no freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.32,main,mion,0,0,0,,except what you're allowed \Nby our rules and directives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.41,main,mion,0,0,0,,Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.12,main,man,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:45.02,main,man,0,0,0,,Let's cut the bullshit already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:49.76,main,mion,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do{\i0} appreciate your kind assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.31,main,mion,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.75,main,mion,0,0,0,,That's my bullet-catching trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.26,main,aki,0,0,0,,So she really can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:10.19,main,mion,0,0,0,,As you can see, I have the \N"turn your hand into a cannon" ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:15.15,main,mion,0,0,0,,And if fact, you've all been \Ngifted similar abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:21.77,main,mion,0,0,0,,In other words, you're our \Nability testing focus group!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.54,main,mion,0,0,0,,We've taken everything from you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.22,main,mion,0,0,0,,and given you a unique ability in exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.64,main,mion,0,0,0,,Please use it to its fullest to run the \Nprogram we've arranged to completion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:33.94,main,mion,0,0,0,,But if we determine you useless \Nfor providing product feedback,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.91,main,mion,0,0,0,,we'll have to ask you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.00,main,mion,0,0,0,,So {\i1}do{\i0} take this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.98,main,mion,0,0,0,,Now I'll explain the program's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.71,main,mion,0,0,0,,First, those cuffs you're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.95,main,mion,0,0,0,,They both restrict your movement and \Nprevent the use of your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.24,main,mion,0,0,0,,When the red lights turn green,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.16,main,mion,0,0,0,,it means they'll unlock in five seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:53.49,main,mion,0,0,0,,and you can use your abilities then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:58.60,main,mion,0,0,0,,You won't be penalized \Nfor any harm or death
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.95,main,mion,0,0,0,,your abilities inflict on \Nother focus group members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.52,main,mion,0,0,0,,This concludes the program's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.66,main,mion,0,0,0,,Any questions? Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:09.88,main,mion,0,0,0,,I'm under the impression \Nyou enjoy games like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.05,main,mion,0,0,0,,Any questions from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.37,main,mion,0,0,0,,Class Representative Ringo Tatara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.99,main,mion,0,0,0,,Won't you be the first with your hand up,\N the way you always are at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.28,main,mion,0,0,0,,Madoka Kirisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.82,main,mion,0,0,0,,You're such a delinquent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.72,main,mion,0,0,0,,and this is a lot like a school lecture, \Nso I guess you might be struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.50,main,mion,0,0,0,,I know absolutely everything, \Nso don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:35.22,main,kuma,0,0,0,,I have a question, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.05,main,mion,0,0,0,,Shin Kumagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.52,main,mion,0,0,0,,Ask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.08,main,kuma,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.60,main,kuma,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.21,main,kuma,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:46.81,main,mion,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}so{\i0} happy you asked, but unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.14,main,mion,0,0,0,,None of those are questions I can answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.10,main,kuma,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.41,main,kuma,0,0,0,,Why did you kill that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:55.98,main,kuma,0,0,0,,With power like yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.75,main,kuma,0,0,0,,you could have easily \Nstopped him non-fatally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:01.69,main,mion,0,0,0,,I know all about you, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:03.77,main,mion,0,0,0,,so I know that you're a really good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.23,main,mion,0,0,0,,But I killed that man because \NI'm a really {\i1}bad{\i0} person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.48,main,mion,0,0,0,,Does that answer your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.13,main,kuma,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.73,main,rin,0,0,0,,It's thoroughly understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.61,main,rin,0,0,0,,We're all dead already anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.97,main,rin,0,0,0,,I'd bet you had that little magic \Nshow planned from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.39,main,rin,0,0,0,,To make a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:23.76,main,mion,0,0,0,,My, you're a clever one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.60,main,mion,0,0,0,,Okay! Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.34,main,yuu,0,0,0,,Um... I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.36,main,mion,0,0,0,,Yuuri Amagake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.74,main,mion,0,0,0,,Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.83,main,yuu,0,0,0,,No one else is asking, \Nso I guess I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.99,main,yuu,0,0,0,,Why did you choose us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.46,main,yuu,0,0,0,,You seem to have learned all about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.00,main,yuu,0,0,0,,What were the criteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.09,main,mion,0,0,0,,What a great question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.78,main,mion,0,0,0,,But you'll find the answer \N{\i1}pretty{\i0} disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.69,main,mion,0,0,0,,We chose you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.13,main,mion,0,0,0,,entirely at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.45,main,mion,0,0,0,,That should take a weight \Noff your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.98,main,mion,0,0,0,,You basically won the lottery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.91,main,mion,0,0,0,,Think of it like a freak \Ntraffic accident that—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.55,top,yang,0,0,0,,Miss Mion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.40,main,yang,0,0,0,,I think it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.36,main,mion,0,0,0,,Oh, Yang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.15,main,mion,0,0,0,,Is it time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.34,main,mion,0,0,0,,The Q&A is over, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:12.53,main,yang,0,0,0,,The first program will be one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.19,main,yang,0,0,0,,A series of simple duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:17.05,main,yang,0,0,0,,I'll lead you all to your rooms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:21.25,main,yang,0,0,0,,You can take that time to learn \Nand practice your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.72,main,mion,0,0,0,,And one last reminder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:30.67,main,mion,0,0,0,,Consider how you should \Napproach this very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.31,sign_18046_185_Akira_Shiroyanag,sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HE60010&\pos(180,155)\fad(1,141)}Absent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.60,sign_18046_185_Akira_Shiroyanag,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,105)}Akira Shiroyanagi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.60,sign_18046_185_Akira_Shiroyanag,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(141,1)\c&H0200BE&\pos(180,155)}Present
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:39.00,main,aki,0,0,0,,This really is going like a game, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.33,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I'm curious about who these people \Nare, what they're after,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:48.58,sign_606_8_Konpeito,sign,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFF4F1&\c&H9272D8&\fs15\pos(310,20)}Konpeito
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.32,italics,aki,0,0,0,,and various other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.54,sign_18428_192_This_room_contai,sign,0,0,0,,{\an7}This room contains a bed, a toilet,\Na refrigerator, objects your ability \Napplies to, ten sheets of paper,\Nand pencils. One-on-one battles end\N through loss of consciousness, death, or\N admittance of defeat. Your ability is written\N on a separate sheet of paper (enclosed).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.63,italics,aki,0,0,0,,But the most important thing right now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.87,sign_18428_192_This_room_contai,sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H282C27&\3c&HF0F4EF&\fs20}This room contains a bed, a toilet,\Na refrigerator, objects your ability \Napplies to, ten sheets of paper,\Nand pencils. One-on-one battles end\N through loss of consciousness, death, or\N admittance of defeat. Your ability is written\N on a separate sheet of paper (enclosed).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.50,italics,aki,0,0,0,,is to find out my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.90,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Receive your conditions and solve \Nthe subsequent puzzles you face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:04.20,italics,aki,0,0,0,,The game's difficulty will vastly change \Nbased on the conditions presented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.22,Your,sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HFDFFF8&\3c&H2D2522&}Your
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.14,Your,sign,0,0,0,,{\fry180}Your
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.82,main,aki,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.27,main,mion,0,0,0,,Oh, Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.55,main,yang,0,0,0,,That same boy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:17.73,main,mion,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.01,main,mion,0,0,0,,He's my personal favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:23.18,italics,aki,0,0,0,,What in the world is this ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.71,italics,aki,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.87,sign_606_8_Konpeito,sign,0,0,0,,{\3c&HF7F2EC&\c&H9D62EB&}Konpeito
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.59,main,aki,0,0,0,,Konpeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.17,main,aki,0,0,0,,The sweetness! It stimulates the brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.19,main,aki,0,0,0,,I guess they really do know me inside and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.12,main,aki,0,0,0,,So much about this feels off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.34,main,aki,0,0,0,,That woman's actions, most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.32,main,aki,0,0,0,,Yes, it's almost like she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.77,sign_20028_214_Time_Until_One_o,sign,0,0,0,,Time Until One-on-One 18:41:37
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.76,main,aki,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:01.08,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Someone testing their ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.52,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That vibration and sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.94,italics,aki,0,0,0,,What if someone with a powerful \Nability tries to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.29,italics,aki,0,0,0,,How could I use my ability to counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.90,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:18.67,sign_20468_220_No_penalty_for__,sign,0,0,0,,No penalty for \Nharm or death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.32,italics,aki,0,0,0,,The things she said... \NThe rules laid out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.66,italics,aki,0,0,0,,From the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.72,italics,aki,0,0,0,,She's been baiting us into killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.08,italics,aki,0,0,0,,An ability focus group? That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.54,italics,aki,0,0,0,,But interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.74,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.25,main,mion,0,0,0,,It's really coming together, Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.74,main,mion,0,0,0,,Such an excellent group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.97,main,mion,0,0,0,,They'll realize it soon, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:45.68,main,mion,0,0,0,,How they should behave, when all \Nthey have is their ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.48,main,mion,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.49,main,mion,0,0,0,,First program!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.93,main,mion,0,0,0,,One-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.05,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.74,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Surprised you too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.02,main,kiri,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.21,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Is he my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.43,main,kiri,0,0,0,,I always hated school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.89,main,aki,0,0,0,,It's him... the one who \Nstruggles with school stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.76,main,kiri,0,0,0,,But it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.33,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Just surrender the second \Nthe battle starts, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.10,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.45,main,kiri,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.81,main,kiri,0,0,0,,That'll save me time and \Nyou a world of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.78,main,kiri,0,0,0,,My ability's just a little nasty, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.17,main,aki,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to see it through, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.53,main,kiri,0,0,0,,You've got some backbone, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.33,italics,ann,0,0,0,,The first program will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.39,italics,ann,0,0,0,,Matches can only be resolved \Nthrough admission of defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.66,italics,ann,0,0,0,,loss of consciousness, or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.87,italics,ann,0,0,0,,Please begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.93,italics,aki,0,0,0,,The cuffs are about to unlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.86,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Once they do, we can use our abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:50.79,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.23,italics,aki,0,0,0,,In five seconds, the battle begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:56.52,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Well, don't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.15,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Let's go, freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.57,italics,aki,0,0,0,,He turned the stick into a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.74,main,kiri,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:51.10,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Sorry, kid! Can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.56,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Just knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.03,main,kiri,0,0,0,,You've got a nice bag of tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.29,main,kiri,0,0,0,,but it's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:05.75,main,yang,0,0,0,,I wonder why he won't use his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:07.93,main,mion,0,0,0,,It's not time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:11.17,main,kiri,0,0,0,,What is that, a barricade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.87,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Maybe you didn't get a \Ngood fighting ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:18.39,main,kiri,0,0,0,,None of us knows what \Nhappens when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:22.36,main,kiri,0,0,0,,So I get how you feel, \Nbut just surrender already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.52,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's what I was waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.72,main,kiri,0,0,0,,You're messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.57,main,kiri,0,0,0,,It's over, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.68,main,kiri,0,0,0,,You've run out of tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.31,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Look, you got dragged into this, same as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:40.41,main,kiri,0,0,0,,I don't wanna make mincemeat \Nout of you if I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.26,main,aki,0,0,0,,That's not the reason I'm \Nnot using my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.36,main,aki,0,0,0,,It's the opposite, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.68,main,mion,0,0,0,,Looks like it's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:52.62,main,kiri,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:53.63,main,aki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:58.10,main,aki,0,0,0,,I'm hesitant to use my ability \Nbecause it's so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.24,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Hesitant because it's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.55,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Quit bluffing, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.29,main,aki,0,0,0,,I'm not bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.01,main,aki,0,0,0,,I think you remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.85,italics,kiri,0,0,0,,Remember... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.02,main,kiri,0,0,0,,If you won't surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.27,main,kiri,0,0,0,,I'll kill you before you can kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.41,main,aki,0,0,0,,The illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.44,main,aki,0,0,0,,My ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:27.58,main,aki,0,0,0,,The "turn your hand into a cannon" ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:36.76,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Yes... I think you saw it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.87,italics,kiri,0,0,0,,The "turn your hand into \Na cannon" ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.12,italics,kiri,0,0,0,,That {\i0}is{\i1} a nasty ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.67,italics,aki,0,0,0,,This is how my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.53,italics,aki,0,0,0,,So the sword reverts to a stick \Nwhen it leaves his hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.08,main,aki,0,0,0,,I guess it's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.74,main,aki,0,0,0,,You've lost your weapon. You can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.48,main,aki,0,0,0,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.48,main,aki,0,0,0,,I'll be forced to shoot you otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:26.63,main,aki,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.57,main,kiri,0,0,0,,You little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.78,main,kiri,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.41,main,kiri,0,0,0,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.56,italics,ann,0,0,0,,The winner, Akira Shiroyanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.82,main,mion,0,0,0,,Like I said, he's worth watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.88,main,yang,0,0,0,,Yes... he was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.45,main,mion,0,0,0,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.74,main,mion,0,0,0,,He used his ability so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:20:00.37,main,yang,0,0,0,,But why did he wait so long to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.97,main,yang,0,0,0,,He could have used that cannon at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:07.67,main,mion,0,0,0,,Did he manage to convince you \Nthe cannon was his ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.61,main,mion,0,0,0,,He created such an interesting illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:14.55,main,mion,0,0,0,,Akira said the cannon was his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.98,main,mion,0,0,0,,But it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.50,main,yang,0,0,0,,What? But I saw him use the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.46,main,mion,0,0,0,,That was the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.62,main,mion,0,0,0,,Akira made use...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.01,main,mion,0,0,0,,of {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:43.34,Your,sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}<<Sophist>>\N\NMr. Akira Shiroyanagi\N\NYour ability is \N"whatever your opponent thinks your ability is."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:43.35,main,mion,0,0,0,,Sophist. "Whatever your opponent \Nthinks your ability is."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:46.63,main,mion,0,0,0,,He needs to arrange the right timing \Nto voice the ability to his opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.24,main,mion,0,0,0,,and create an environment \Nwhere they'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.26,main,mion,0,0,0,,"My ability is 'cannon.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.37,main,mion,0,0,0,,He arranged the conditions \Nand timed it just right
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.76,main,mion,0,0,0,,to make sure his words were believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.98,main,mion,0,0,0,,You're all that I hoped,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.31,main,mion,0,0,0,,my sweet prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.27,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I made it through that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:12.31,italics,aki,0,0,0,,But there's a lot about this \Nability I still need to test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.78,italics,aki,0,0,0,,One's ability determines the \Ngame's content and difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.04,italics,aki,0,0,0,,That's the part that makes \Nthis ability interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.30,italics,aki,0,0,0,,I'll start by doing as they wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.02,italics,aki,0,0,0,,playing through their \Nprogram using my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:31.03,italics,aki,0,0,0,,Then I'll make that cat woman \Nregret ever giving it to me.
